                <mxCell id="60" value="• All Application Pods connect to:&#xa;  - RDS PostgreSQL (read/write)&#xa;  - ElastiCache Redis (caching)&#xa;&#xa;• Monitoring Stack:&#xa;  - Prometheus scrapes all pods&#xa;  - Promtail ships logs to Loki&#xa;  - Tempo collects traces&#xa;  - Grafana visualizes all data&#xa;  - CloudWatch receives metrics&#xa;&#xa;• Load Balancer distributes traffic&#xa;  evenly across all 3 AZs" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=10;fontColor=#000000;" vertex="1" parent="1">
